name: IllegalClassFormatException
comment:
Thrown by an implementation of
 {@link java.lang.instrument.ClassFileTransformer#transform ClassFileTransformer.transform}
 when its input parameters are invalid.
 This may occur either because the initial class file bytes were
 invalid or a previously applied transform corrupted the bytes.

constructors.name: IllegalClassFormatException
constructors.comment: Constructs an IllegalClassFormatException with no detail message.

constructors.name: IllegalClassFormatException
constructors.comment: Constructs an IllegalClassFormatException with the specified detail message.
